Class SpiraBuilder.DescriptorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • hudson.model.Descriptor<BuildWrapper>
      • com.inflectra.spiratest.plugins.SpiraBuilder.DescriptorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Saveable
    Enclosing class:
    SpiraBuilder

    @Extension
public static final class SpiraBuilder.DescriptorImpl
extends Descriptor<BuildWrapper>
    Descriptor for SpiraBuilder. Used as a singleton. The class is marked as public so that it can be accessed from views.

    See src/main/resources/hudson/plugins/hello_world/SpiraBuilder/*.jelly for the actual HTML fragment for the configuration screen.
